sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>Controller NS
    participant Route as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Predictor as Predictor Service<br/>8080/8443 TCP
    participant NIMAPI as NVIDIA NIM API<br/>api.ngc.nvidia.com<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MR as Model Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,Predictor: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment (RawDeployment)
        User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (InferenceService)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>Auth: SA Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>Auth: SA Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>Auth: SA Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterRoleBinding<br/>Auth: SA Token
        Note over Route,Predictor: External access established
        User->>Route: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS TLS Edge/Reencrypt
        Route->>Predictor: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8080 or HTTPS/8443
        Predictor-->>Route: Prediction result
        Route-->>User: JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService Auth Setup (RHOAI 3.x)
        User->>K8sAPI: Create LLMInferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (LLMInferenceService)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Read Gateway (openshift-ai-inference)<br/>Auth: SA Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Gateway AuthPolicy (Kuadrant)<br/>Auth: SA Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute AuthPolicy (Kuadrant)<br/>Auth: SA Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create EnvoyFilter (Istio TLS bootstrap)<br/>Auth: SA Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Roles/RoleBindings for KEDA<br/>Auth: SA Token
    end

    rect rgb(245, 255, 230)
        Note over User,NIMAPI: Flow 3: NIM Account Setup
        User->>K8sAPI: Create NIM Account CR<br/>(with API key secret ref)
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (Account)
        Controller->>NIMAPI: Validate API key<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / API Key Bearer
        NIMAPI-->>Controller: Validation result
        Controller->>NIMAPI: Fetch model catalog<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ / API Key Bearer
        NIMAPI-->>Controller: Model catalog JSON
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap (model list)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create pull secret (NGC registry)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Template (NIM serving)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 245)
        Note over Controller,MR: Flow 5: Model Registry Sync
        Controller->>MR: Sync InferenceService metadata<br/>HTTPS TLS / Bearer Token
        MR-->>Controller: Registry metadata
    end
